Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.76,0:11:01.27,Text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}もういいやってそっぽ向いて　にわか雨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.27,0:11:09.44,Text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}逃げだした背に一筋の虹がかかるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.07,0:11:16.53,Text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}君の声が
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.53,0:11:22.70,Text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}この手取って　光射す方へと
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.70,0:11:27.92,Text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}君が連れ出してくれた闇から
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.92,0:11:33.51,Text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}どんな未来(あす)も　恐れずに行けるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.51,0:11:36.32,Text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}「繋いだ手、離さない」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.32,0:11:42.64,Text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}微笑んで　君は言った
Dialogue: 1,0:10:44.75,0:10:50.34,Text-ch-top,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}「我不會放棄喜歡的事」
Dialogue: 1,0:10:50.34,0:10:55.28,Text-ch-top,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}我不再能挺起胸膛說出這句話
Dialogue: 1,0:10:55.76,0:11:01.27,Text-ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}驟雨之中我說著算了 轉過身去
Dialogue: 1,0:11:01.27,0:11:09.44,Text-ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}逃避的背影之上 一道彩虹架起
Dialogue: 1,0:11:12.07,0:11:16.53,Text-ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}是你的聲音
Dialogue: 1,0:11:16.53,0:11:22.70,Text-ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}拉著我的手 前往光芒的方向
Dialogue: 1,0:11:22.70,0:11:27.92,Text-ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}是你帶我走出了黑暗
Dialogue: 1,0:11:27.92,0:11:33.51,Text-ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}所以不論怎樣的未來 我都能坦然面對
Dialogue: 1,0:11:33.51,0:11:36.32,Text-ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}「我不會放開這牽起的手」
Dialogue: 1,0:11:36.32,0:11:42.64,Text-ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}你微笑著說道
Comment: 0,0:12:33.63,0:12:38.20,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,---------------------------IN「STAND BY YOU」------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.52,0:12:38.77,Text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}愛の歌　ほら唄い出す
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.77,0:12:44.77,Text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}君の心解かすまでね
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.77,0:12:49.85,Text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}隠してたメロディ　私歌うから
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.85,0:12:54.75,Text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}茶化したりはしないでね　you know？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.99,0:13:00.53,Text-jp-top,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}ないものねだりの先に
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.53,0:13:06.31,Text-jp-top,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}２人の今描いてゆける
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.31,0:13:11.34,Text-jp-top,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}困った時には支えるから
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.34,0:13:17.76,Text-jp-top,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}信じて欲しい　側にいるよ　be with you
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.76,0:13:27.47,Text-jp-top,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}キラリ　星に舞う　涙の軌跡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.47,0:13:32.00,Text-jp-top,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}痛みを越えて　ぎゅっと抱きしめて
Dialogue: 1,0:12:33.52,0:12:38.77,Text-ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}唱響這首愛之歌
Dialogue: 1,0:12:38.77,0:12:44.77,Text-ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}直到解開你的心結
Dialogue: 1,0:12:44.77,0:12:49.85,Text-ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}曾被埋沒的旋律 由我來歌唱
Dialogue: 1,0:12:49.85,0:12:54.75,Text-ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}你可不許笑我喔 you know？
Dialogue: 1,0:12:54.99,0:13:00.53,Text-ch-top,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}儘管可能只是鏡花水月
Dialogue: 1,0:13:00.53,0:13:06.31,Text-ch-top,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}但我們兩人可以不斷描繪
Dialogue: 1,0:13:06.31,0:13:11.34,Text-ch-top,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}困難之時會有我支持你
Dialogue: 1,0:13:11.34,0:13:17.76,Text-ch-top,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}請你相信我 我會在你身邊 be with you
Dialogue: 1,0:13:17.76,0:13:27.47,Text-ch-top,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}閃閃發亮 星辰舞動 淚水軌跡
Dialogue: 1,0:13:27.47,0:13:32.00,Text-ch-top,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}跨越傷痛 緊緊抱在懷中吧
Comment: 0,0:00:43.02,0:00:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,------------------------------OP「Now On Air」----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.27,0:00:46.82,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}夢の続きをリライト
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.82,0:00:50.20,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}聞こえますか？未来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.20,0:00:55.58,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}君と声を重ねて届ける
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.58,0:01:04.34,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}はじまりのナンバー　夢にとどけ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.34,0:01:09.47,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}平坦な道　探して
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.47,0:01:12.76,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}進むことに飽きたの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.76,0:01:15.76,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}叶えても　叶うだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.76,0:01:20.73,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}夢はなぜこの手で　形を変えてくの？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.73,0:01:26.77,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}教えて　どれくらい？　頑張れば辿り着くの…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.77,0:01:32.07,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}理想につぶれてた　私はもういない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.45,0:01:35.53,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}夢の先をリライト
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.53,0:01:38.75,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}掴みたいよ未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.75,0:01:46.13,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}君と声を重ねて　届けるの　もっと先へ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.13,0:01:49.21,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}ひとりじゃ歩けない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.21,0:01:52.38,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}景色　君とみてみたい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.38,0:01:55.68,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}ひとりじゃ進めない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.68,0:01:58.31,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}直感を信じて生きてたい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.31,0:02:01.39,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}夢の先の New World
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.39,0:02:04.65,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}聞こえていますか？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.65,0:02:08.57,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}この声が終わるまで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.57,0:02:12.45,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}君に伝え続けるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.27,0:00:46.82,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}重寫夢想的續集
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.82,0:00:50.20,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}會聽到未來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.20,0:00:55.58,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}我們的聲音重疊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.58,0:01:04.34,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}送出的開場曲 飛向夢想吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.34,0:01:09.47,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}總是尋找平坦的路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.47,0:01:12.76,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}只會讓我厭倦前進
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.76,0:01:15.76,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}就算去實現 也只是完成
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.76,0:01:20.73,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}夢想為何會因為這隻手改變形態呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.73,0:01:26.77,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}請告訴我 還要努力多久才能到達
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.77,0:01:32.07,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}曾經只能仰視理想的我 已經改變
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.45,0:01:35.53,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}重寫夢想的延續
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.53,0:01:38.75,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}希望把握住未來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.75,0:01:46.13,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}我們的聲音重疊 直抵更遠方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.13,0:01:49.21,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}一個人走不下去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.21,0:01:52.38,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}想和你一同欣賞美景
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.38,0:01:55.68,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}一個人無法前進
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.68,0:01:58.31,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}希望能追隨直覺活著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.31,0:02:01.39,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}夢想前方的新世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.39,0:02:04.65,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}你聽清楚了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.65,0:02:08.57,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}直到無法發聲為止
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.57,0:02:12.45,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}我都會一直為你開口
Comment: 0,0:22:04.97,0:22:08.14,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,---------------------------ED「STAND BY YOU」------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.14,0:22:13.52,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}Stand by me, you did that
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.52,0:22:16.15,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}Stand by you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.36,0:22:26.08,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}気持ち伝えるのにいつも何故　こんなにも悩み
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.08,0:22:29.25,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}ゆらり揺れている
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.25,0:22:36.00,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}本当は君が好きなのに　うらはらで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.00,0:22:39.67,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}上手く言えないよ　ねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.59,0:22:42.38,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}振り返れば
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.84,0:22:45.55,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}君が映る
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.64,0:22:49.31,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}目と目合わせ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.31,0:22:54.40,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}愛の歌　そう唄い出す
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.40,0:23:00.61,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}君にいつか届くまでね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.61,0:23:03.20,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}大事にしてたフィーリング
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.20,0:23:05.66,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}全部込めるから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.66,0:23:10.66,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}ちゃんと受け止めてくれるよね？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.66,0:23:15.92,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}真夜中のラブソングで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.92,0:23:21.88,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}世界がちょっと変わってほしい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.88,0:23:27.26,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}そして君とsweetie　2人ぼっち
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.26,0:23:29.93,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}100ミリちょっとの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.93,0:23:32.02,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}隙間埋める
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.02,0:23:33.85,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}be with you
Comment: 0,0:22:08.14,0:22:13.52,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,Stand by me, you did that
Comment: 0,0:22:13.52,0:22:16.15,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,Stand by you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.36,0:22:26.08,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}只是表明心意 為什麼讓我如此煩惱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.08,0:22:29.25,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}總是搖擺不定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.25,0:22:36.00,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}其實那麼喜歡你 卻言不由衷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.00,0:22:39.67,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}找不到合適的話語
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.59,0:22:42.38,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}回首身後
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.84,0:22:45.55,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}眼中有了你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.64,0:22:49.31,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}我們四目相對
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.31,0:22:54.40,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}唱響這首愛之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.40,0:23:00.61,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}希望有一天你能聽到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.61,0:23:03.20,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}一直珍惜的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.20,0:23:05.66,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}都包含其中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.66,0:23:10.66,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}你一定會接受它吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.66,0:23:15.92,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}願這首午夜小情歌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.92,0:23:21.88,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}可以讓世界稍微改變
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.88,0:23:27.26,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}然後與你甜甜蜜蜜 二人世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.26,0:23:29.93,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}十多公分的間隙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.93,0:23:32.02,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}全都被填滿
Comment: 0,0:23:32.02,0:23:33.85,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,be with you
